sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant vLLM as vLLM API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    participant HPU as Intel Gaudi HPU<br/>In-process
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as Model Storage<br/>(PVC / S3)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Inference Request
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (RBAC)
        Proxy->>Proxy: Validate RBAC authorization
        Proxy->>vLLM: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 (localhost, pre-authenticated)
        vLLM->>HPU: Submit inference batch<br/>In-process (HPU graph execution)
        HPU-->>vLLM: Inference result<br/>In-process
        vLLM-->>Proxy: JSON response<br/>HTTP/8000
        Proxy-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/8443
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 1a: Model Loading (startup)
        vLLM->>HF: GET model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: HF Token (env var)
        HF-->>vLLM: Model artifacts
        vLLM->>S3: Load model from PVC/S3<br/>(alternative to HF Hub)
        S3-->>vLLM: Model weights
        vLLM->>HPU: Transfer weights to HPU memory
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Multi-Card Distributed Inference (Tensor Parallelism)
        participant Ray as Ray Head
        participant W0 as HPU Worker rank 0
        participant W1 as HPU Worker rank 1..N
        vLLM->>Ray: Initialize distributed workers
        Ray->>W0: Assign rank 0
        Ray->>W1: Assign rank 1..N
        W0->>W1: HCCL all-reduce / all-gather<br/>HCCL fabric (no encryption)
        W1-->>W0: Collective results
        W0-->>vLLM: Merged inference output
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Disaggregated Serving (NIXL KV Transfer)
        participant Prefill as Prefill Instance<br/>HPU
        participant NIXL as NIXL Agent<br/>Network
        participant Decode as Decode Instance<br/>HPU
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/completions
        Proxy->>Prefill: Forward to prefill instance
        Prefill->>NIXL: Transfer KV cache<br/>NIXL protocol (no encryption)
        NIXL->>Decode: Deliver KV blocks<br/>(block size conversion if heterogeneous)
        Decode-->>Proxy: Generate tokens → response
        Proxy-->>Client: Streaming response
    end
